    <item>
      <title>由于红海袭击扰乱全球流动，石油价格将每周上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-22/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-22</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于红海的新袭击促使数百艘船只选择更安全但更长的航线，导致大规模延误并扰乱了全球流量，油价延续了两个月来的最大单周涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-22/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-22</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 00:11:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
